data.description: Charming home in Park hill with 3 bedrooms, 1.5 updated baths, original hardwood floors & original tile in bathroom. Cozy updated kitchen with granite counters & stainless steel appliances. Stain glass in bedroom & entryway. Large deck overlooking spacious backyard that is fenced with storage building. Roof & HVAC replaced  in last couple of years. Centrally located in the heart of Fort Smith. Fireplace is plumbed for gas but owner has never used it.
